{"tid":2091120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【白紙。文宣行動】——以白紙對抗白色恐怖","createTime":"2020-07-02T14:23:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T20:37:31.000Z","uid":271792,"like":54,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"999e0f01bcc62ba4cfcce18743ce848913967f34","tid":2091120,"uid":271792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T14:23:02.000Z","msg":"【白紙。文宣行動】&mdash;&mdash;以白紙對抗白色恐怖<br />\n<br />\n7月1日，手足因為攜帶文宣貼紙被捕，<br />\n7月2日，多間黃店被恐嚇移除文宣。<br />\n港區國安法通過首兩日，<br />\n#白色恐怖&mdash;&mdash;我地已經避無可避。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「白色恐怖」</span></span><br />\n白色恐怖一詞源自法國大革命。當時以白色為代表的保皇黨人為震懾異議份子，便透過利用一些制度性的機制來侵害人權，例如透過法律手段來進行威脅、打壓或迫害，透過受控制的輿論來進行威嚇，甚至訴諸武力、暗殺、或任意使用權力，以維護既定的權力格局。<br />\n<br />\n既然如此，不如以白色對抗白色？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【白紙。文宣行動】</span></span><br />\n<br />\n⚪️目的：表達對国安法下白色恐怖的不滿<br />\n⚪️好處：成本更低/攜帶白紙風險較低<br />\n<br />\n⚪️行動：與貼紙師相似，手足準備一疊白紙，以膠紙/blu-tack痴喺唔同地方。<br />\n例如：交通工具、連儂牆、黃店⋯<br />\n<br />\n//連儂牆上寫什麼不是重點。<br />\n香港人不用細看，已知道想要表達的什麼。<br />\n「真正重要的，用眼睛看不見。」 &mdash;小王子//<br />\nNo Boundary CWB-Haven - Facebook<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人未驚過。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n#白紙文宣行動"},{"pid":"3d7325011346c2f63871248414c061697d7aae6a","tid":2091120,"uid":271792,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T14:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/66hijXw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F66hijXw.jpg&h=0d2bd43d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tvXx8QS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtvXx8QS.jpg&h=075ed747&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N8F7XKd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN8F7XKd.jpg&h=fe4c9143&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q47x8QU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq47x8QU.jpg&h=c2856734&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d536ab8b6ff3f5fd15cdaa07d1afe8786a179f57","tid":2091120,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T14:24:21.000Z","msg":"所有黃店即換上《紅》文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2090968\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2090968</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a66e72524e00adb78877784540fab2737ae4fb63","tid":2091120,"uid":34196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T14:31:22.000Z","msg":"十連"},{"pid":"caa6147a36f9720303f68ff52dbe068ac045024a","tid":2091120,"uid":34196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T14:31:34.000Z","msg":"九連"},{"pid":"c823e33d9201d2830cceec3e12dd1217fd452bdb","tid":2091120,"uid":34196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T14:31:49.000Z","msg":"八連"},{"pid":"5899dbaf071f85800c3c6525f81f756cc99b7d1f","tid":2091120,"uid":34196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T14:32:01.000Z","msg":"七連"},{"pid":"b21196432d7d62c5b9d16c42e5a7d1caae3b7e1a","tid":2091120,"uid":266503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T14:32:23.000Z","msg":"「人民不應該害怕他們的政府，政府應該害怕它的人民。」（People should not be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.）<br />\n<br />\n「藝術家用謊言揭露真相，政治家用謊言掩蓋真相。」（Artists use lies to tell the truth, while politicians use them to cover the truth up.）<br />\n<br />\n「沒有舞蹈的革命，是不值得發動的革命。」（A revolution without dancing is a revolution not worth having）<br />\n<br />\n「面具之下只是個血肉之軀，而在這面具之下的，還有一個理念，只不過，理念，是刀槍不入的。」（Beneath this mask there is more than flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea, Mr.Creedy, and ideas are bulletproof..）<br />\n<br />\n「我們的尊嚴可能不值錢，但它卻是我們唯一真正擁有的東西。它是我們最後一寸領地，但在那一寸領地裡，我們是自由的。」（Our integrity sells for so little, but it is all we really have. It is the very last inch of us, but within that inch, we are free）<br />\n<br />\n「力量來自團結，團結來自信念」（Strength through unity, unity through faith）<br />\n<br />\n「恐懼往往是政府的終極武器。」（Fear became the ultimate tool of this government）<br />\n<br />\n「就算政府擁有的武力統治不讓人民發言，自由的言論仍然充滿著強大的力量。」（the truncheon may be used in lieu of conversation, words will always retain their power)"},{"pid":"928d184bc95850463aeaeae439ff3f306e03a4b9","tid":2091120,"uid":49370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T14:32:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86820878cef12965cd221fc9da61b268103191f3","tid":2091120,"uid":34196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T14:32:53.000Z","msg":"斷咗 繼續推"},{"pid":"a3d3f036e367734e95036c2d24d8815e3debeaf8","tid":2091120,"uid":293543,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T14:33:20.000Z","msg":"會唔會俾藍絲寫晒支持立國安法，習近平萬歲架"},{"pid":"d8b741de300fea77af39373dd9aa811edb71f384","tid":2091120,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T14:34:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://today.line.me/tw/pc/article/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E3%80%8C%E8%88%89%E7%99%BD%E7%B4%99%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E3%80%8D+%E6%8F%AD%E6%8A%97%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%80%E6%B2%88%E7%97%9B%E3%80%81%E6%9C%80%E7%84%A1%E5%A5%88%E3%80%81%E6%9C%80%E6%9C%89%E5%8A%9B%E7%9A%84%E5%90%B6%E5%96%8A-k5va9L\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2Ftw%2Fpc%2Farticle%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%2588%2589%25E7%2599%25BD%25E7%25B4%2599%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E3%2580%258D%2B%25E6%258F%25AD%25E6%258A%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%25B2%2588%25E7%2597%259B%25E3%2580%2581%25E6%259C%2580%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25A5%2588%25E3%2580%2581%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%258A%259B%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%2590%25B6%25E5%2596%258A-k5va9L&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBAp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=dd53e05f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ht