E7%9A%84%E5%90%B6%E5%96%8A-k5va9L\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2Ftw%2Fpc%2Farticle%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%2588%2589%25E7%2599%25BD%25E7%25B4%2599%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E3%2580%258D%2B%25E6%258F%25AD%25E6%258A%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%25B2%2588%25E7%2597%259B%25E3%2580%2581%25E6%259C%2580%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25A5%2588%25E3%2580%2581%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%258A%259B%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%2590%25B6%25E5%2596%258A-k5va9L&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBAp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=dd53e05f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/tw/pc/article/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E3%80%8C%E8%88%89%E7%99%BD%E7%B4%99%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E3%80%8D+%E6%8F%AD%E6%8A%97%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%80%E6%B2%88%E7%97%9B%E3%80%81%E6%9C%80%E7%84%A1%E5%A5%88%E3%80%81%E6%9C%80%E6%9C%89%E5%8A%9B%E7%9A%84%E5%90%B6%E5%96%8A-k5va9L</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n舉白紙抗議"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T14:36:09.000Z","msg":"少女說，過去都會在現場舉標語，通常都是到場後隨便派隨便拿那種，今天是國安法第一天，她不知道要舉甚麼才不會犯法。<br />\n<br />\n記者寫道，她突然想起，<span style=\"color: red;\">以前看過的蘇聯冷笑話：紅場上，有個人在派傳單，軍官到場把人逮捕，卻發現傳單都只是白紙。軍官想了想，對那個人說：「你以為我不知道你想寫甚麼？」</span><br />\n少女說，「我突然想看看，看起來荒謬的笑話，是不是已經成真了。」"},{"pid":"231be37189a9d538c1160776f66d28b6cc0b2353","tid":2091120,"uid":12319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T14:36:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"445536477a8aa4dba594c7ad402f15cc4515bfb2","tid":2091120,"uid":70417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T14:37:55.000Z","msg":"畫公仔記得畫晒啲內臟出黎<br />\n唔係啲官唔識睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bc13126d304b38604f63a2322d04516a6d5dc14","tid":2091120,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T14:38:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">白紙行動</div></